Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How could you run off frigh~tened
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:06.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When they all needed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:11.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To leave them 'neath the spell, abandon all you once knew
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:14.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And after all that's hap~pened
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just you alone are free
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:22.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But what more can I do, then turn my tail and flee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I've lived a simple life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm no one great or migh~ty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What more could I have done
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:39.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Who would the hero rightly be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:42.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The hero I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:51.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Protect the humble and weak
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If only I could find~ one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A warrior or mage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:04.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or even search for him, the greatest wizard of this age
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But who would wish to come
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To save our lowly town
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:14.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When monsters hide in every shadow that is found
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But how would they all hide
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:20.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If light could shine for all to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:28.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Why find a single knight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When we could have an army be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:35.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The heroes I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:43.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To fight what evil may wreak
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:29.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If they'd only hear my plea
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Far be~yond the Sirens
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:38.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just imagine what could be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:53.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We would stand the vanguard against anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Every battle could be won
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:07:00.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When they'd need~ us we would be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:04.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,United, as guardians to save everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:10.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,History is full of evils left astray
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Like a plague upon the world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:19.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Darkness we could finally seal away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We could forge something great
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:29.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Protect all those who are in need
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Each foe would know their fate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:40.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As righteous Pillars they could be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The heroes I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:49.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To stand when all else looks bleak
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:55.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To save the vanquished and meek
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:08:02.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The heroes I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:47.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She came, demanding tribute
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:52.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Our harvest hers to consume
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:56.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As our hunger continued
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:01.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It seemed she'd be our doom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:06.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There was no one to stop her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:11.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This Sphinx a beast so daunting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:16.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yet still our Prince would be stirred
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To resist her taunting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:24.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The beast was displeased
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:30.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Snatched him away to her temple lair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:34.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For him to be freed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:39.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her riddle must be solved if we dare
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All we know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:45.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All we owe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:49.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All that shines as the Glowpaz glows
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All from faith
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:57.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All from Hope~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:08.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I knew it was my doing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:13.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,From such an innocent alm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:18.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Quickly I galloped after
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:23.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I knew I must save Hi~san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She asked me the phrase
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:32.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,One simple riddle with all at stake
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:36.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then, I would elate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:42.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I knew the answer without mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The sphinx scrunched up her wicked face
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To hear the answer found
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She roared and said "you'll know your place"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then stomped against the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"But the riddles' solved!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:06.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"You're not absolved"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She said with leering eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:11.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"Your bounty still belongs to me"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her word, a hollow lie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:16.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I could not leave the Prince in chains
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And let her steal from everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"But what about another game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A challenge all or none"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"But if I win you'll go away
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And leave our village be"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The Sphinx intrigued said: "We shall see"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then laughed aloud in glee
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Blind and without wings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:20.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She had me cross that most dangerous pool
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I made the leap
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:30.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I held to Hope like a precious jewel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All we know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All we owe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:39.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All that shines as the Glowpaz glows
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All from faith
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All from Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I was blessed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I still owe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:54.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could tell you "no"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I will come
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:14:01.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Bring them Hope~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As but a colt
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I would work in the fields
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:35.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Of our peaceful seaside realm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Wishing one day
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I could be strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:42.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To join the~ Mighty Helm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I was small
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Not muscled or tall
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:54.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Twas a thing I might never be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Shovel in hoof
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I set out to prove
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That they would have a place for me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With what strength I could find
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I worked hard as I might
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:08.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Twas a dream I would never let go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With all body and mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Through the day and the night
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I refused to relent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Til I made that dream so
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Our village laid place
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,At a volcano base
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:27.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Never once had we seen it blow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then on that day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:30.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We found we would face
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The~ wrath of its fiery glow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We had no way to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All the lava we saw
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:41.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the Helm said we had to go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But despite all our fright
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We just couldn't withdraw
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We could not leave our homes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the land that we know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:08.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The river of lava got closer and closer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:12.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Soon to consume everything that we were
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:15.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I could do little but had to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:19.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So shovel in hoof I dug into the dirt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:23.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Digging the trench all my efforts seemed foolish
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:27.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Weak as I was I would run out of time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I needed a strength that would meet my ambition
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:34.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When there in a flash happened something divine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With what I'd been blessed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I carved out the trench
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:32.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And was able to save the town
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The lesson I learned
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Was still to endure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:39.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When it seems all is com~ing down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With Great Strength you can find
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That no matter the fight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You can beat almost every foe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:49.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With your brethren combined
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to smite
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Every villain that you couldn't face (just alone)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With the Helm at my side
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We protected our land
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And with them that will still be so
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:04.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For these Sirens may try
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But they're standing in sand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'll knock them aside
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:11.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed I will go~~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:26.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Deep here in the Hayseed Swamp
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We've lived a long 'ol time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Doin' our best to get along
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With all the critter life
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:35.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Our masks and stews all simple but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's peaceful and sublime
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:39.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Never had too much hardship or
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Even a little strife
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:43.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Til the folks fell sick
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With all these horrid spots
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Coughing up with bubbles
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:51.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sneezing lightning snot
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:54.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cough, pop, zap and boom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The plague was spreading way too soon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:58.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cough, pop, zap and boom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I feared it'd be our doom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:03.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If I could not mix a healin' brew
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The fever'd claim me too
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With no one left to do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'd say adieu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Every old elixir and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Each potion I could find
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Didn't change that accursed plant
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or poison that's inside
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When soon it claimed my mother too
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In bed she slept maligned
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:34.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I stared down in the bayou to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,See if that'd provide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:38.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Me the answer to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:41.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Save everyone I loved
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When some flash bees flew out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:46.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hovered just above
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:48.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,​Cough, pop, zap and boom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The flowers opened up their plumes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:52.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cough, pop, zap and boom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And spread their toxic fumes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:57.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But the flash bees were left unamused
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:59.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And took the pollen too
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:01.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And that is when I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:03.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What I must do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:15.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,After many tries
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.83,0:23:18.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And far too many stings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:20.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I did realize
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:22.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just what would be the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:24.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For my healin' mask
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:27.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Looked like the flash bee queen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:29.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Let me take their honey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:32.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Without gettin' mean
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:37.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cough, pop, zap and boom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.03,0:23:40.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,One by one and room to room
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:42.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cough, pop, zap and boom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.30,0:23:44.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The honey once consumed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:46.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Healed them all up quick, shooed away the gloom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:48.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We drank the healin' brew
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.05,0:23:50.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And all escaped the tomb
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.81,0:23:53.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But now… not much I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.55,0:23:55.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Unless you need a potion brewed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:57.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I've done my due
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:23:59.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To see our problems through
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:02.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If you really think you need me too
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:04.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll pack some different brews
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.80,0:24:06.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And help you to undo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:07.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The Sirens' gloom
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.16,0:26:14.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Being just a Legion grunt
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.78,0:26:17.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I traveled wherever they needed me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.40,0:26:19.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And although the pegasi do rule the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.99,0:26:21.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The job ain't that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.56,0:26:23.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But it's not the griffons or the hippogriffs
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.11,0:26:25.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That give us much to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.72,0:26:27.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When one of those giant stinking dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.05,0:26:31.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Gets a little bit too near~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.51,0:26:35.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Every tempest you may see~
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.94,0:26:39.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,None shall stay thee
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.88,0:26:43.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Knowing you are called to be
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:49.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.84,0:26:51.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No matter what the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.53,0:26:53.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forged so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.41,0:26:55.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If it tries to kill you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.69,0:26:58.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Show your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.31,0:26:59.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's them who won't be
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.85,0:27:03.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.71,0:27:13.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then on such a mission
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.91,0:27:15.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We did have to get
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.26,0:27:16.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Across the dragon lands
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.88,0:27:18.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When we saw two of them large enough
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.83,0:27:20.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To wrap us in a single hand
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.08,0:27:22.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Many of our comrades were ensnared
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.14,0:27:25.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And taken back into their cave
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.20,0:27:26.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I could not just leave them like that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.92,0:27:30.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There must be a way that we can save~!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.88,0:27:34.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Like feathers in a wing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.41,0:27:38.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'd be nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.35,0:27:42.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And as one be ascending~
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.76,0:27:49.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.28,0:27:50.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Out from the cave I led them
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.92,0:27:53.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forged so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.85,0:27:54.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As they tried to roast me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.12,0:27:57.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Show your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.86,0:27:59.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With the shield I could be
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.33,0:28:03.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.76,0:29:07.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As the storm was gathering
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.26,0:29:11.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Full of lightning
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.24,0:29:15.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You'll not be cowering
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.71,0:29:24.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.19,0:29:25.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Somehow we really made it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.88,0:29:28.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forged so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.88,0:29:29.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Like the shield we all could
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.04,0:29:32.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Show your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.81,0:29:34.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Play the role we all should
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.24,0:29:38.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brave enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.47,0:29:40.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You've got guts
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.95,0:29:42.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To pull this all together
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.64,0:29:44.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.49,0:29:46.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yes I'm gonna join you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.80,0:29:49.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They'd be~ nuts
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.46,0:29:50.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If they think they could beat
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.00,0:29:55.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.54,0:31:12.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All my life I saw the goodness in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.06,0:31:18.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In the great and little~ things
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.55,0:31:24.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I had strived to bring more everywhere I could
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.08,0:31:30.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Like a flower in the~ spring
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.14,0:31:34.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yet I was so unconscious of
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.40,0:31:37.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where ugliness could cling
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.62,0:31:41.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where such a pain might have fes~tered
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.89,0:31:46.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where I was need~ed to bring~~
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.36,0:31:50.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,True beauty inside
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.00,0:31:53.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Not seeking glory
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.44,0:31:56.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Trying to justify
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.08,0:32:00.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I had let decay~
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.46,0:32:04.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So~ long
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.54,0:32:12.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,After years I found my village left in ruin
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.03,0:32:17.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How I felt like such a~ fool
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.55,0:32:24.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That I'd let her steal all beauty that she could
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.00,0:32:31.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To create an empty~ jewel
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.06,0:32:34.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And what I found there upon the throne
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.33,0:32:36.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In her abhorrent rule
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.59,0:32:41.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Was an old friend I cared about
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.81,0:32:47.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I had let her turn so cruel~~
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.11,0:32:51.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All beauty outside
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.83,0:32:53.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Filling the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.22,0:32:57.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All an attempt to hide
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.64,0:33:07.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A curse born from an en~vious pride~~
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.58,0:33:10.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How our village cried
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.29,0:33:13.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I should have seen
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.46,0:33:16.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The cause of this great divide
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.33,0:33:21.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now I had to face~ her
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.49,0:33:25.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For beauty isn't ours a~lone
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.33,0:33:30.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A thing to steal or hoard or own
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.24,0:33:35.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It is a light for all to~ see
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.08,0:33:42.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A well of life to let flow~ free
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.72,0:34:10.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And in the end, when I held her there
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.99,0:34:13.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I knew I had to prove
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.25,0:34:17.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Give up my beau~ty for everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.66,0:34:23.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And e~ven her too~~
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.72,0:34:31.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,True beauty inside
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.40,0:34:34.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Shines on its own
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.76,0:34:37.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All vanity aside
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.47,0:34:47.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Frees those who let u~gliness hide~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.15,0:34:51.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All I could provide
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.82,0:34:53.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.00,0:34:57.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To help out your vil~lage too
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.82,0:35:01.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll do it to help~
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.32,0:35:05.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You~~
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.16,0:37:10.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So now you've heard each story we~ could tell
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.06,0:37:16.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And what has brought me to you as~ well
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.11,0:37:23.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My village left bewitched beneath~ their song
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.75,0:37:31.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With every passing day, it prolongs~~
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.61,0:37:34.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Everyone I know and love
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.80,0:37:37.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cursed to be their slaves
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.44,0:37:41.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We could bring the Si~rens down
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.85,0:37:45.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We could save
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.26,0:38:35.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I sympathise what you've en~dured
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.78,0:38:38.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But you know not what you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.00,0:38:42.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And know not its al~lure
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.90,0:38:47.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All of my students come to~ learn
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.45,0:38:51.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That all sorcery is power
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.56,0:38:54.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Which demands that you dis~cern
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.79,0:39:00.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You collect them like torches to burn a fire~ bright
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.09,0:39:06.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But think not what to do when you too ignite
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.64,0:39:09.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When forged by life, what we can create
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.01,0:39:13.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is all but a candle compared to the fates
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.76,0:39:18.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But you wish to take their power for your own
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.28,0:39:22.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When forged divine, a magic runs deep
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.69,0:39:25.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,An ocean whose edges that we'll never see
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.40,0:39:29.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You know not the costs such sorcery
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.59,0:39:33.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Could rise from the unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.54,0:39:53.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Respectfully, you must believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.82,0:39:57.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That these gifts that they~ were granted
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.05,0:40:00.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Are branches of~ a tree
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.10,0:40:06.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I think of them more like the~ sun
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.50,0:40:10.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Not a group of little torches~
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.65,0:40:13.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But a light for every~one
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.76,0:40:19.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or as beams in a rainbow of every colored light
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.10,0:40:25.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Who could end e~very storm and be glowing bright
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.54,0:40:28.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They're forged as one, whatever you say
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.95,0:40:32.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All elements of something come from the fates
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.74,0:40:37.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You can see it for yourself or turn away
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.25,0:40:41.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For all you've done, the spells you have penned
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.59,0:40:44.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The things that will shape ponykind to its end
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.38,0:40:48.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yet you disavow this chance we have
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.53,0:40:52.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause of what we might pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.06,0:41:07.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I know I should have died that day
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.25,0:41:11.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,By dragon fire or lightning yet
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.44,0:41:14.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We found that we could do much more
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.51,0:41:17.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When greater challenges are set
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.85,0:41:20.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd failed my home and kin
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.81,0:41:23.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But from the state that things were in
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.04,0:41:26.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We turned the darkness back and
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.78,0:41:30.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Found the answer hiding deep within
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.41,0:41:33.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,While fear once al~most held me back
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.49,0:41:36.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sit around and mope
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.68,0:41:39.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I had to take the leap and
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.45,0:41:45.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Put my trust in hope
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.57,0:42:00.07,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Alright, I've heard you make your~ case
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.09,0:42:03.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It is clear to me these wonders
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.24,0:42:07.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Must have a higher~ place
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.25,0:42:12.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And since you'll do it either~ way
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.69,0:42:16.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With a sorcerer~ to guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.88,0:42:19.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You might not go as~tray
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.06,0:42:22.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There indeed is much darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.21,0:42:25.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That we could cast away
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.32,0:42:28.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To a place they'd be left
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.91,0:42:34.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To decay~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.06,0:42:38.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So forged as one, with firmament laid
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.47,0:42:41.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'll rise up as Pillars protecting the gates
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.15,0:42:47.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For all who may need us on that day
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.66,0:42:50.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And forged as one, we'll keep building high
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.04,0:42:54.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,These gifts for all creatures to come for all time
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.71,0:42:57.07,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And bring Harmony to all
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.30,0:43:04.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Who have been left in dismay~~